## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf-linker/parallel/typepool">TypePool</a> keeps type descriptors which contain partially cloned <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/die">DIE</a> correspinding to each type.

Types are identified by names.
